latestIgtvVideos.title: cure PCOS/PCOD in 4 steps!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
share this video someone might need it!🙏
Women with PCOS produce higher-than-normal amounts of male hormones.it causes them to skip periods and makes it harder for them to get pregnant.

🚫Foods to avoid:
 sugar 🍰
 Dairy products 🥛
 soy products 
 Refined carbs 🍚
 white bread/rice/pasta
 soft drinks 
 Any food that comes in packet.

⭕Foods to consider
  High fiber food🥗
 whole wheat
  green veggies🥦
 fruits 🍎
 oats/upma
  brown rice 
  Chicken/eggs 🥚
